<hr><a name="a23"></a><sel><font color="#009933">Other Improvements</font></sel><p></p>
<p>The logic of search in the list names has changed. The new version will execute the search when you choose the condition "search area - in the list document names" in the Basic Search, i.e. a new list is generated on the basis of the initial one, consisting of the documents meeting the new request.</p>
<p>The Basic Search panel is activated immediately at system entry, without additional cursor placing in the search string with the click of the mouse or from the keyboard.</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="c1"></a><h3>
Sending the Documents over E-Mail
</h3>
<p>
An opportunity to send document text over e-mail directly from GARANT System has been implemented. When you press the button Send by e-mail on the toolbar, a new message is created with an attached file containing the text of the document concerned.
</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="c2"></a><h3>
Vivid Depiction of Various Types of Links
</h3>
<p>
Special cursors are used to mark the links to the document invalidated, not yet entered into force or absent in the user set, as well as the Internet links. When you move the cursor of the link, it will change to inform you which object is "on the other end" of the link. 
</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="e1"></a><h3>
Sending the Lists over E-Mail
</h3>
<p>
If you press the toolbar button Send by e-mail while working with a list, a new message will be generated with an attached file containing the list of documents concerned. It is possible to send both the whole of the list and selected elements only.
</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="e2"></a><h3>
Drag-and-Drop Saving of List Documents in My Documents
</h3>
<p>


You can save list <hint><font color="#009933">elements</font>
	(<font color="#808080">documents</font>)
</hint> in My Documents by simply dragging them with the mouse from the Main Window with the list to the navigation panel tab without invoking a special dialogue box.
</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="e3"></a><h3>
Permanent Use of Filters
</h3>
<p>
An opportunity to set up automatic use of filter to all generated lists has been implemented, permitting to exclude, as a result, from them the documents failing to meet the conditions specified in the filter used automatically. 
</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="b2"></a><h3>
Failure-to-Get-a-Reply Warning because of the Absence of Connection
</h3>
<p>
A special mechanism of diagnostics and user warning has been developed for operative notification of the impossibility because of the technical reasons (e.g. absence of or unstable Internet connection) to get a reply to a question to the Online Legal Support Service.  
</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="g2"></a><h3>
New Look of the System Entry Dialogue Box
</h3>
<p>
GARANT System entry dialogue box has been made simpler. Its design is more convenient and understandable. The new dialogue box suggests vividly two alternatives - login for registered users and creation of a new account. The latter is supplied with an explanatory text and a link for registration.
</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="g3"></a><h3>
Automatic Determination of the Optimal Size of Buttons
</h3>
<p>
An intellectual mechanism has been implemented to determine the optimal system appearance depending on the user monitor resolution. An average size icons regime has been implemented in addition to large and small icons.

</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="g4"></a><h3>
User Notification of Invalid Entry in the Context Filter and Search-by-Details Fields
</h3>
<p>
System response has been improved in the cases of entry of a nonexistent value in the Context Filter field or Search-by-Details card. As soon as the entered value no longer meets all available details, a signal is played, and the entered values are painted red. The new algorithm does not permit to enter new invalid characters in the filter field, signalling to correct the entry.
</p>
<h4><com id="main"><a href="#main" title="Cсылка на топик main"><font color="#0000ff">Home</font></a></com></h4><a name="g6"></a><h3>
Notification of Users Working with Single-User Network Options
</h3>
<p>
If you try to log in a single-user network set "occupied" by another specialist, the system will issue a message indicating the name of the working user. 
</p>
